{
  "stem": "24615.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she died, and she was-- we couldn't bury her, because they had to get a [INAUDIBLE] from the German, from the head German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- I forgot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, I forgot a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, but a commandant-- they had a commandant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a storm trooper, or whatever you call them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was laying, like, seven days, you know, on the floor til we got allowed to bury her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and the Judenrat sent a guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he was sitting with me, you know every day and every night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, after she got buried, you know, neighbors came, you know, in and out, and some were sitting with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think in a week, or two weeks, a month, you know, they rounded up all the Jewish people, and they chased them into the ghetto, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was all Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't see no Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was like a seven mile-- it was a bridge, like what the water used to go through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they threw down one guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if he didn't work too fast or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they threw him down in the water, I don't know how you'd survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the back was a way that what they could go to right in the back of our house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Ukrainian-- you know, man or woman, they were running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were hitting them with chains, with sticks, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One lady, a young lady, you know, they hit with a stick, and I think it was a nail in it, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the blood was coming out and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they closed up-- they closed up the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every-- every-- then I started going-- going to work, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
